<br>
/attack off<br>
/do skill 1 (pick pocket location)<br>
/do skill 2 (Hide location)<br>
/attack on<br>
<br>
Simple, just keep fighting and popping the key. Skill up and no agro all the while getting exp.<br>
<br>
The issue of whether you tell your group about it is another one altogether and i won't even get into it. Suffice to say if you are honest and tell them you are working it for epic and will hand over words/gems etc people are fine with it.<br>
